&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and contribute as part of a cross-functional Agile team to design, develop, and maintain web and mobile applications using React, React Native, TypeScript, JavaScript, &lt;a href=&quot;http://node.js/&quot;&gt;Node.js&lt;/a&gt;, Ruby on Rails, Git, and related technologies, applying modern software architecture principles and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead software architecture and design to support MHV project needs, leveraging best practices including modularity, scalability, accessibility, and seamless EHR integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align engineering best practices across multiple delivery teams (which may include establishing an Engineering Community of Practice within the contract, and/or ensuring consistent engineering standards are met across the portfolio).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish strong relationship with your VA counterparts.&lt;/li&gt;
